<text><body>
<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">淳化鎮積善菴</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">公產</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">田地塘</cb:mulu>
<milestone unit="juan" n="12"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0175b11"/><cb:mulu type="卷" n="12"></cb:mulu><cb:juan fun="open" n="12"><cb:jhead>金陵梵剎志卷十二</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="B" n="0175b12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">三禪寺</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">中剎</note>三禪寺<note place="inline">古剎</note></head>
<lb ed="B" n="0175b13"/><p xml:id="pB29p0175b1301" style="margin-left:1em">在郭城鳳臺門外東城盡節鄉北去所統靈谷寺一百
<lb ed="B" n="0175b14"/>二十里聚寶門一百二十里所領小剎曰安平寺登臺
<lb ed="B" n="0175b15"/>寺慈光寺無垢寺紫草寺華嚴寺</p>
<lb ed="B" n="0175b16"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">殿堂</cb:mulu><head>【殿堂】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">山門</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0175b1603" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">山門<note place="inline">參楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">左觀音殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0175b1607" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">左觀音殿<note place="inline">伍楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">右輪藏殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0175b1613" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">右輪藏殿<note place="inline">參楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">僧院</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0175b1619" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">僧院<note place="inline">參房</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">基址陸畝</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0175b1623" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">基址陸
<lb ed="B" n="0175b17"/>畝<note place="inline">東至朱家山　南至劉家山　西至劉家山　北至范家山</note></p></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0175b18"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">公產</cb:mulu><head>【公產】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">田地山塘</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0175b1803" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">田地山塘<note place="inline">共壹百捌拾伍畝肆分</note></p></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0175b19"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">安平寺</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">小剎</note>安平寺</head>
<lb ed="B" n="0175b20"/><p xml:id="pB29p0175b2001" style="margin-left:1em">在郭城外東城盡節鄉南去所領三禪寺十五里北去
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B29.0160.0176a" n="0176a"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0176a01"/>聚寶門一百五里乾道志有安平院在下橋村今或本
<lb ed="B" n="0176a02"/>此</p>
<lb ed="B" n="0176a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">殿堂</cb:mulu><head>【殿堂】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">佛殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176a0303" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">佛殿<note place="inline">參楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">僧院</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176a0307" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">僧院<note place="inline">貳房</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">基址參畝</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176a0311" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">基址參畝<note place="inline">東至韓村　南至遊方橋　西至劉家山　北
<lb ed="B" n="0176a04"/>至馬溪橋</note></p></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0176a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">公產</cb:mulu><head>【公產】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">田地塘</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176a0503" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">田地塘<note place="inline">共壹拾捌畝陸分</note></p></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0176a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">登臺寺</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">小剎</note>登臺寺</head>
<lb ed="B" n="0176a07"/><p xml:id="pB29p0176a0701" style="margin-left:1em">在郭城外東城盡節鄉南去所領三禪寺十里北去聚
<lb ed="B" n="0176a08"/>寶門一百里</p>
<lb ed="B" n="0176a09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">殿堂</cb:mulu><head>【殿堂】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">佛殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176a0903" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">佛殿<note place="inline">參楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">法堂</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176a0907" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">法堂<note place="inline">伍楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">僧院</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176a0911" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">僧院<note place="inline">壹房</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">基址捌畝</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176a0915" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">基址捌畝<note place="inline">東至社塘冲南至門塘冲
<lb ed="B" n="0176a10"/>西至積田冲北至茅塘冲</note></p></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0176a11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">公產</cb:mulu><head>【公產】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">田地山塘</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176a1103" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">田地山塘<note place="inline">共貳拾貳畝伍分</note></p></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0176a12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">慈光寺</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">小剎</note>慈光寺<note place="inline">古剎</note></head>
<lb ed="B" n="0176a13"/><p xml:id="pB29p0176a1301" style="margin-left:1em">在郭城鳳臺門外東城盡節鄉張橋村南去所領三禪
<lb ed="B" n="0176a14"/>寺二十里北去聚寶門一百一十里乾道志有慈光院
<lb ed="B" n="0176a15"/>在章墅村去城百里疑即此</p>
<lb ed="B" n="0176a16"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">殿堂</cb:mulu><head>【殿堂】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">山門</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176a1603" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">山門<note place="inline">參楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">正佛殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176a1607" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">正佛殿<note place="inline">參楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">法堂殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176a1612" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">法堂殿<note place="inline">伍楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">僧院</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176a1617" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">僧院<note place="inline">壹房</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">基址伍畝</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176a1621" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">基址伍畝<note place="inline">東至
<lb ed="B" n="0176a17"/>龍母山　南至新庄山　西至章橋村　北至雁灘山</note></p></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0176a18"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">公產</cb:mulu><head>【公產】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">田</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176a1803" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">田<note place="inline">共貳畝貳厘</note></p></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0176a19"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">無垢寺</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">小剎</note>無垢寺<note place="inline">古剎</note></head>
<lb ed="B" n="0176a20"/><p xml:id="pB29p0176a2001" style="margin-left:1em">在郭城鳳臺門外道德鄉東城北去所領三禪寺五里
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B29.0160.0176b" n="0176b"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0176b01"/>北去聚寶門一百二十五里原先朝天喜寺梁天監二
<lb ed="B" n="0176b02"/>年改無垢寺乾道志又名無垢院　國朝重修如今額</p>
<lb ed="B" n="0176b03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">殿堂</cb:mulu><head>【殿堂】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">山門</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176b0303" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">山門<note place="inline">參楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">佛殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176b0307" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">佛殿<note place="inline">參楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">左觀音殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176b0311" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">左觀音殿<note place="inline">參楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">右輪藏殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176b0317" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">右輪藏殿<note place="inline">參楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">僧院</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176b0323" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">僧院<note place="inline">貳房</note></p></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0176b04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">基址伍畝</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176b0401" style="margin-left:2em">基址伍畝<note place="inline">東至伍菴庄　南至來龍山　西至磨盤山　北至胡家店</note></p></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0176b05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">公產</cb:mulu><head>【公產】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">田地山塘</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176b0503" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">田地山塘<note place="inline">共陸拾陸畝參分肆厘</note></p></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0176b06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">紫草寺</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">小剎</note>紫草寺<note place="inline">古剎</note></head>
<lb ed="B" n="0176b07"/><p xml:id="pB29p0176b0701" style="margin-left:1em">在郭城夾岡門外東城道德鄉北去所領三禪寺十里
<lb ed="B" n="0176b08"/>北去聚寶門一百二十里係唐古剎　國初重建殿宇
<lb ed="B" n="0176b09"/>經燬嘉靖間募修</p>
<lb ed="B" n="0176b10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">殿堂</cb:mulu><head>【殿堂】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">佛殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176b1003" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">佛殿<note place="inline">參楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">僧院</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176b1007" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">僧院<note place="inline">壹房</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">基址拾畝</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176b1011" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">基址拾畝<note place="inline">東至石秋壩　南至桑園圃　西至挑洪街
<lb ed="B" n="0176b11"/>　北至銅山</note></p></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0176b12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">公產</cb:mulu><head>【公產】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">田地山</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176b1203" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">田地山<note place="inline">共貳拾參畝玖分</note></p></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0176b13"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">華嚴菴</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">小剎</note>華嚴菴</head>
<lb ed="B" n="0176b14"/><p xml:id="pB29p0176b1401" style="margin-left:1em">在郭城外東城道德鄉北去所領三禪寺十里北去聚
<lb ed="B" n="0176b15"/>寶門一百二十里</p>
<lb ed="B" n="0176b16"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">殿堂</cb:mulu><head>【殿堂】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">山門</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176b1603" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">山門<note place="inline">參楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">地藏殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176b1607" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">地藏殿<note place="inline">參楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">觀音殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176b1612" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">觀音殿<note place="inline">參楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">僧院</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176b1617" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">僧院<note place="inline">壹房</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">基址貳畝</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0176b1621" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">基址貳畝<note place="inline">東至
<lb ed="B" n="0176b17"/>溧水塘　南至本寺山　西至至吳家山　北至武家山</note></p></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>